question link: https://practice.geeksforgeeks.org/problems/wave-array-1587115621/1

Solution:
class Solution {
    public static void convertToWave(int n, int[] a) {
        // code here
        int temp=0;
        int i=0;
        while(i<n-1)
        {
            temp=a[i];
            a[i]=a[i+1];
            a[i+1]=temp;
            i+=2;
        }
    }
}
